title: Girls with Slingshots - Complete Run, 2004-2015 {WebComixFan}
description:
"GIRLS WITH SLINGSHOTS" Web Comic

"Girls with Slingshots" (girlswithslingshots.com) by Danielle Corsetto primarily centers around friends Hazel Tellington and Jamie McJack, following their daily lives as they deal with various events such as unemployment, marriage and sexuality.  Story lines are typically humorous in nature, but occasionally brush against more serious topics.  The series has received praise for its depiction of LGBTQ characters and characters with disabilities.

This torrent collects the full run of "Girls with Slingshots" comics, from the strip's beginning in September 2004 to its conclusion in March 2015.  The CBR files in the set correspond to the published (or soon-to-be published) volumes of the comic, but they are NOT scans of the books; all the comics in this torrent were downloaded directly from the girlswithslingshots.com Web site
